Description: Provides tools for bioinformatics modeling using recursive 
    transformer-inspired architectures, autoencoders, random forests, 
    XGBoost, and stacked ensemble models. Includes utilities for 
    cross-validation, calibration, benchmarking, and threshold optimization 
    in predictive modeling workflows.
